() Tj
T*
(WSL) Tj
T*
(Import full-i3 with scripts/install-wsl-distro.sh --distro Ooonana --tarball) Tj
T*
(/var/tmp/ooonana-os/release/ooonana-full-i3-wsl-rootfs.tar.gz --force) Tj
T*
(Launch with: wsl.exe -d Ooonana -- /usr/bin/start-ooonana-i3) Tj
T*
(WSL GUI needs WSLg or an X server with DISPLAY set.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(AI) Tj
T*
(Ooonana AI runs as ooonana ai ... or ooonana-ai. It supports provider setup, model) Tj
T*
(aliases, ask/chat, tools, tasks, audit, history, status, and the full-i3 ooonana-ai-) Tj
T*
(app launcher.) Tj
